summary: This is my take on Link for a Racemenu Preset
descriptionHtml:
this is actually the character i am using in my LOZ play through that i keep talking about. i just thought it would be nice to upload it as it took me a whopping 4 and a half hours to make! he is a wood elf in v1 and a breton in v2

[size=4]DO NOT LEAVE HATE IN THE COMMENTS. I'D LIKE TO SEE YOU GUYS SPEND HOURS ON END CREATING STUFF FOR OTHERS AND HAVE PEOPLE REPLY THAT IT IS F***** UP AND THE UGLIEST THING YOU SAW. IF YOU DONT HAVE ANYTHING NICE TO SAY THEN KEEP IT TO YOURSELF.[/size]

Required
